{"tid":2261733,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG谷] 90/00後初級開心行山谷！！！！","createTime":"2020-10-28T14:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T20:27:42.000Z","uid":42217,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4afbc40feaedce1fe46d7e34b762129e3515e165","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"呢家秋天涼涼地，各位巴絲有冇興趣一齊行吓山? <br />\n<br />\n我諗住開個全新既行山谷，等所有巴絲可以放心吹水同參加行山團，唔洗因為D人熟咗而面左左，唔敢放心開懷傾計同開團。巴打絲打亦要互相尊重，有厹或娘娘會即踢。<br />\n<br />\n如果有興趣開開心心搵吓朋友仔一齊行山，歡迎填妥google form、亦可以係留言留低tg id，有足夠人數我將會係一星期內開谷:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeDO2_-465fVz2MOHFnxy8rr7cAc35AlmPJTPw7rHeeo1kw3A/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeDO2_-465fVz2MOHFnxy8rr7cAc35AlmPJTPw7rHeeo1kw3A%2Fviewform&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7DYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=56f19562\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeDO2_-465fVz2MOHFnxy8rr7cAc35AlmPJTPw7rHeeo1kw3A/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以開開心心一齊行山，體驗香港既另一面! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53158dc83353d3e782858dec08b96cc30a42ae9a","tid":2261733,"uid":307877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"初級即係會行邊啲山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122c4a1e1d82c1310cfbeb94656baffa2173e968","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"53158dc83353d3e782858dec08b96cc30a42ae9a","tid":2261733,"uid":307877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"初級即係會行邊啲山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:22:29.000Z","msg":"初級會分為一星至五星路線，<br />\n一星你預輕輕鬆鬆行吓郊遊徑、水塘 (e.g. 城水 / 大潭水塘 / 千島湖)，<br />\n二至三星就行吓要少少體力既路線 (e.g. 獅子山 / 西貢昂平 / 菠蘿山),<br />\n四至五星就行進階路線 (e.g. 大東鳳凰、鎖羅盆荔枝窩、蛇尖狗牙嶺)<br />\n<br />\n開咗谷之後，大家有咩地方想行都可以開團架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2c23296467b95cfd27618c23e831fb2d5df5d1","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a217ce098b8c477d623dcc1e4fb381e0703a858a","tid":2261733,"uid":210944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"add5cf3d1058b8b9abc12d7cb685b727f44c739c","tid":2261733,"uid":369470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"cf26a28c73744f0a226730ca52b5fe8cea5194f4","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:13:52.000Z","msg":"lmmm"},{"pid":"e8afc17c8eba45819b5efc7f3871b5cbca2e7189","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43246f98d85380312c9a51645fd48136f4f38843","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"push，越嚟越多巴絲報咗名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5839b3086d4107fbc4e1ac3e363113f38da1286","tid":2261733,"uid":101801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2536ecc3b80e0dd4e64c3abadd41eba3c04323e9","tid":2261733,"uid":82457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"122c4a1e1d82c1310cfbeb94656baffa2173e968","tid":2261733,"uid":42217,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"53158dc83353d3e782858dec08b96cc30a42ae9a","tid":2261733,"uid":307877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"初級即係會行邊啲山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:22:29.000Z","msg":"初級會分為一星至五星路線，<br />\n一星你預輕輕鬆鬆行吓郊遊徑、水塘 (e.